,Recommended,434570,21911257,"Posted: 18 March, 2016",all,ghidorah45,"Blood and Bacon is a gory and fantastically enjoyable and relaxing experience in which you will gun down thousands upon thousands of pigs on a farm over 101 levels. Overtime, you will unlock several unique weapons and acquire comical powerups from a functional pig grinder on the farm. Although it seems straightforward at first, the variety in the games levels will always be a challenge; just as you set into a rhythm, the game throws several new enemy types upon you, forcing you to stay on your toes. The pig types include armored pigs, super fast pigs, tiny pigs, huge pigs, skeletal pigs, princess pigs, pigs that run in herds, pigs that can grow in size, and many other types that can be tricky to deal with when first encountered. Each of the game's weapons, from an uzi to a missile launcher, feel powerful and satisfying to play with. At its low price, there are very very few games on any platform that can match Blood and Bacon in value, fun, and comedy. I have gotten more entertainment out of this game than games that cost 60 times its value, and I highly recommend it as a casual shooter to play through."
