,Recommended,434570,26356914,"Posted: 1 November, 2016",all,-<TSG>- Velociforce,"time for my review of this game, oh boythis game is a very entertaining mess, what i mean by that i will explain.this game in my overall oppinion is not really too good, but it can be very fun to play for a few hours, if you pick up this game dont let it gather dust due to negative reviews, the reason being that there is actually fun to be had in this game, the graphics are bad as hell ill admit but there is no reason to hate a game due to graphic and visual stuff, well unless it's really bad.this game has a focus on gameplay, i know your probably laughing at that but I'm going to break down what this game is in my review for this game.well the positives are:the enemies, hear me out they are pigs, but its great to get away from the zombie games and have something else take the spotlight for once as a mutated mess, and pigs are a suprisingly fun idea, you can run around shooting them like regular zombies exept they generally take alot more hits than in zombie games, the reason being beyond me but its still funthe weapon selection aint that great, but is still pretty good compaired to some other games, you have these weapons to use:-Colt 1911-357 Magnum-paintgun (yup for real)-silences XDM (correct me if im wrong about that one)-shotgun-M4A1-AK47-UZI-P90-and a strange nuke deviceas far as im aware thats all the guns that are available to use in the game.their is an item system to this game, and a way to purchase items during a level using pigs meat, believe it or not this is done using a grinder, of which somehow turns it into ammo and items to purchache using the ammount of meat present in the machine, this mechanic is something you dont get often, not unique but still something good to seeyou can play with 2 players, and up to 4 (or 6 in the halloween update) but when this was posted this feature is still in beta, alough from my testing it so far works pretty well, i love playing with friends in this game, and when its not with friends, their is suprisingly good community with the others who you can get into games with.the gameplay is often smooth, this game does not require a lot of processes and actually very little, meaning on even a craptop this game can reach a constant 60FPS, or more.as their is positives their is also negatives:their is only a single map to play on, it may be a pretty good map but it is small, and rather repetitive and dull after a while, a good map variety or progression of maps would be cool to have, but their just isnt that.their are only 2 bosses present in the game, which you face every 10 days, the time to face them isnt bad but the variety is poor, you would expect their to be different, more cretive bosses every 10 days but it just goes back and fourth between 2, known as princess and the brother or brothers after the first 10 days, a better variety would be apriciated in a game like this.their isnt much dialogue, only the farmer really talks, and he says some ridiculouse jokes, i just think maybe their could be some lines for your characters to say, i wont push this as a very negative just something that i think could make a improovmenttheir is no story to this game to my knowledge, a good story is always cool even for a survival game, where you can come across things that tell you about the past of the events in this game, but currently their is none, only what happens from day 1, again just a feature that would make the game better not something that ruines the game entirelyin conclusion i think this game is pretty fun, definatly good value for the current selling price, this is why i will give this game a definate up rating, even if it isnt fun forever its still a good laugh for up to 5 hours! if you enjoy it longer than that then thats great!7/10"
