,Not Recommended,434570,33724819,Posted: 22 July,all,The Fla╯╰mer | GameTame.com,"When I first bought the game I was a bit happy because I saw that you could kill a lot of pigs and that was kind of funny. Now I am disappointed with the game, and I will tell you why :The first levels are ok, but later, it becomes repetitive and boring. All you have to do is talk to the farmer, kill pigs and thenthe same thing that you do at the beginning of every level. Not to mention that there is nothing interesting while playing the game, except killing pigs and repeat the same thing until day 101. I don't even know why they put another level after the final boss, and in the last day all you have to do is to kill non-zombie pigs. Despite the game focuses at the beginning on saving the farm, because of day 101, you will then discover that you need to sabotage it.Weapons unlock kind of hard, and some of them are way too weak. Also, not to forget, the reloading animations are messed up. The reloading system is very buggy, you can reload even when your weapon's magazine is full.Pigs are kind of durable and overpowered, especially the small ones which run very fast. Weapons do very little damage to them, and they are hard to hit. Also, at some point, you will become overwhelmed, and you need to be an expert just to handle the numerous pigs, even at days 10-30.Bosses are very weird coded. The 1st boss's attacks are very easy to dodge, and he is very slow. But oddly, extremely durable, and you need a lot of bullets to kill him.I definitely do not reccomend this game, which is full of bugs and unbalanced weapons. If you wasted and euro on buying this game, better refund it, but if you like it, I don't blame you.I refunded it and happily I got the money.Do not buy it."
